summary:
PERSIAN DUTCH NETWORK is an independent socio-cultural network which is dedicated to introduce Persian (Iranian) culture in The Netherlands and also making Dutch and Persians more closer to each other.
PDN also tries to help Persian community in Holland to be more familiar with various aspects of Dutch culture and society.
Persian Dutch Network has no political and religious affiliation. The network has been registered at The Netherlands Chamber of Commerce (KvK) under the number:
34374520 0000
( www.persiandutch.com )
